h2. Prerequisites

h3. For Deployment
* Kubernetes 1.24+ (8 CPU, 16GB RAM minimum)
* Splunk Observability Cloud account
* kubectl and helm CLI tools

h3. For Development
* Docker and Docker Buildx
* Python 3.8+
* Git and GitHub account

