h2. FAQ

{panel:title=Can I use this in production?|borderStyle=solid|bgColor=#f0f0f0}
This is a *demo application*. It's designed for learning, workshops, and demonstrations—not production workloads.
{panel}

{panel:title=How do I update to the latest version?|borderStyle=solid|bgColor=#f0f0f0}
Download the latest manifest from [Releases|https://github.com/splunk/opentelemetry-demo/releases] and redeploy with {{kubectl apply}}.
{panel}

{panel:title=What if I don't have AppDynamics?|borderStyle=solid|bgColor=#f0f0f0}
AppDynamics is optional. The demo works fully with just Splunk Observability Cloud. Services with {{optional: true}} for AppDynamics secrets will start without them.
{panel}

{panel:title=Can I deploy just some services?|borderStyle=solid|bgColor=#f0f0f0}
Yes, but some services depend on others (e.g., checkout depends on payment, shipping, email). See [ARCHITECTURE.md|https://github.com/splunk/opentelemetry-demo/blob/main/ARCHITECTURE.md] for dependencies.
{panel}

{panel:title=Where can I get Splunk Observability Cloud credentials?|borderStyle=solid|bgColor=#f0f0f0}
See [DEPLOYMENT.md - Splunk Observability Cloud Setup|https://github.com/splunk/opentelemetry-demo/blob/main/DEPLOYMENT.md#splunk-observability-cloud-setup] for detailed instructions.
{panel}

